## 3. Optimal Chunk Size & Overlap by Content Type

| Content Type                       | Optimal Size     | Overlap       | Rationale                   |
| ---------------------------------- | ---------------- | ------------- | --------------------------- |
| Narrative (articles, essays)       | 300–500 tokens   | \~50 tokens   | Preserves flow + detail     |
| Technical docs (APIs, code, legal) | 100–200 tokens   | Minimal       | Queries target specifics    |
| Research/scientific papers         | 500–1,000 tokens | Section-based | Arguments span paragraphs   |
| Conversational logs                | Semantic turns   | N/A           | Better by dialogue segments |

